===Etymology===
[[zap]] + [[-er]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# (''colloquial'') A [[remote control]] for a [[television]].
#:''This channel is lame.  Hand me the '''zapper'''.''
# A thing that zaps by passing a large voltage, e.g. a [[bug zapper]].
# ''(figurative):'' By extension, any thing capable of extermination.

